Banckle,is,a,cloud,based,software,company,that,offers,businesses,with,online,customer,support,services,Banckle,Campaign,is,an,email,marketing,platform,available,through,Banckle,enabling,businesses,to,connect,with,their,customers,via,campaigning,The,Banckle,Campaign,API,lets,developers,to,personalize,their,customers,experience,by,integrating,it,with,their,applications,enabling,them,to,interact,with,customers,directly,from,the,application,The,API,allows,features,such,as,creating,managing,sending,and,tracking,emails,and,newsletter,campaigns